author: Pearl Buck
message: You cannot make yourself feel something you do not feel, but you can make yourself do right in spite of your feelings.
title: Thought of the day

author: Mary Kay Ash
message: Those who are blessed with the most talent don't necessarily outperform everyone else. It's the people with follow-through who excel.
title: Thought of the day

author: Albert Einstein
message: Try not to become a man of success, but rather try to become a man of value.
title: Thought of the day

author: Lao Tzu
message: All difficult things have their origin in that which is easy, and great things in that which is small.
title: Thought of the day
